OL,3,CHistory behind legendary locomotive
OL,4,CThe Flying Scotsman as she returns
OL,5,Csouth
OL,7,FShe is iconic and known the world
OL,8,Fover, and this week the Flying
OL,9,FScotsman has returned to Hampshire.
OL,11,FBut what is so special about the steam
OL,12,Flocomotive and why do thousands of
OL,13,Fpeople flock to see her?
OL,15,FWhere it began
OL,17,FBuilt in 1923 in Doncaster costing
OL,18,F#7944 the steam locomotive was known
OL,19,Fas the Flying Scotsman after being
OL,20,Fdeployed on the 10am run from London
OL,21,FKings Cross to Edinburgh.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
