PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773609119
OL,3,CHistory behind legendary locomotive
OL,4,CThe Flying Scotsman as she returns
OL,5,Csouth
OL,7,FIt went into service on 24 February
OL,8,F1923 with number 1472.
OL,10,FIt was designed by Sir Nigel Gresley
OL,11,Fas part of the A1 class - the most
OL,12,Fpowerful locomotives used by the LNER
OL,13,Fat that time.
OL,15,FBy 1924, when it was selected to
OL,16,Fappear at the British Empire
OL,17,FExhibition in London, the loco had
OL,18,Fbeen renumbered 4472.
OL,20,FShe was the most powerful engine of
OL,21,Fher day.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
