OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773609119
OL,3,CHistory behind legendary locomotive
OL,4,CThe Flying Scotsman as she returns
OL,5,Csouth
OL,7,FThe locomotive hit the headlines for
OL,8,Fbeing the first to run at 100 miles an
OL,9,Fhour and traveling a non-stop record
OL,10,Fof 422 miles.
OL,12,FThe Flying Scotsman was withdrawn from
OL,13,Fservice in 1963, after 40 years of
OL,14,Fservice.
OL,16,FIn 2004, she was purchased by the
OL,17,FNational Railway Museum, and restored
OL,18,Fto working order in 10 years, costing
OL,19,F#4.2 million.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
