PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773609119
OL,3,CHistory behind legendary locomotive
OL,4,CThe Flying Scotsman as she returns
OL,5,Csouth
OL,7,FWork started in 2006, and a decade
OL,8,Flater she returned to the tracks with
OL,9,Fthousands turning out to see her.
OL,11,FThe next chapter in the Flying
OL,12,FScotsman story was its triumphant
OL,13,Freturn as a working museum exhibit,
OL,14,Fconquering yet another record as the
OL,15,Foldest mainline working locomotive on
OL,16,FBritain's tracks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
