PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773609119
OL,3,CHistory behind legendary locomotive
OL,4,CThe Flying Scotsman as she returns
OL,5,Csouth
OL,7,FThe Flying Scotsman was officially the
OL,8,Ffirst locomotive to circumnavigate the
OL,9,Fglobe and still holds the world record
OL,10,Ffor a non-stop run in a steam
OL,11,Flocomotive, set in 1989 with a 422-
OL,12,Fmile trip.
OL,14,FToday she remain an icon of her era
OL,15,Ftraveling all over the country wowing
OL,16,Fthe crowds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
